info.headline: Flood Watch issued March 22 at 4:35AM PDT until March 23 at 2:00AM PDT by NWS Oxnard
info.description: ...FLOOD WATCH REMAINS IN EFFECT THROUGH THIS AFTERNOON... * WHAT...Flooding caused by excessive rainfall continues to be possible. * WHERE...Most of Los Angeles, Ventura, Santa Barbara, and San Luis Obispo Counties. * WHEN...Through this afternoon. * IMPACTS...Extensive street flooding and flooding of creeks and rivers are possible. * ADDITIONAL DETAILS... - http://www.weather.gov/safety/flood
info.instruction: You should monitor later forecasts and be alert for possible Flood Warnings. Those living in areas prone to flooding should be prepared to take action should flooding develop.
